ExpSyntax.val: MlsTrans('Process in Queing. Please Refresh Journal')

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT FISCAL_YEAR,PERIOD_NO,JOURNAL_DT,JOURNAL_NO FROM GL_JURNALH H (NOLOCK) WHERE H.CO_ID=':1' AND H.BR_ID=':2' AND FISCAL_YEAR=:3 AND PERIOD_NO=:4 AND H.JOURNAL_DT BETWEEN ISNULL(':5',H.JOURNAL_DT) AND ISNULL(':6',H.JOURNAL_DT) AND H.JOURNAL_NO BETWEEN ISNULL(:7,H.journal_no) AND ISNULL(:8,H.journal_no) and journal_id=':10' AND H.STATUS=iif(':9'='P','O','P') AND F_APPROVED=1
